<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Şifre Sıfırlama Hatası | TuMeal</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f6f8fa;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .error-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(44,62,80,0.08);
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem 2rem;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 3rem auto;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .error-card h4 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .error-card p {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .error-icon {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .btn-orange {
            background: #ff6b35;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-orange:hover {
            background: #e55d2a;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #ff6b35;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            color: #ff6b35;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: #ff6b35;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-5 pt-5">
        <div class="error-card">
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle error-icon"></i>
            <h4>Şifre Sıfırlama Hatası</h4>
            <p>Şifre sıfırlama bağlantısı geçersiz veya süresi dolmuş. Lütfen yeni bir şifre sıfırlama talebi oluşturun.</p>
            
            <div class="mt-4">
                <a href="/forgot-password" class="btn btn-orange">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-key me-2"></i>Yeni Şifre Sıfırlama Talebi
                </a>
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline mt-3">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>Giriş Sayfasına Dön
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/js/all.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>